					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">I was looking at my EQCompendium and i found an item that is worn on your neck and is Necromancer and Shadowknight only, and gives +7 Intelligence and +7 Agility and weighs .3 and no armor class. It says it is obtained through a quest in Neriak. Since it is SK/Nec only I think it would start in 3rd quarter at the necro guild. I have no clue on where to get this quest, only that it is in Neriak somewhere and I dont know how to do it but I really want to know. Can anybody help me on how to get this quest, where to get this quest, and how to do this quest? Any ideas? 
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
