			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Ok here is what needs to be done.  You have to get 4 items to give to the GNOME necro.  He asks for a crystaline orb from the stone spider in Solusek B.  He wants a white/gold necklace off some lvl 40ish froggie in Guk (not sure which one I just bought mine for 500 pp) You need a drop of blood off of some chick at the druid ring in Rathe Mnts.  It cannot be taken by force must be taken willingly SOOOO you have to go to Permafrost and kill an icy terror and get a prickly pear off it.  She is indifferent and will not agro you.  Give her the pear she &quot;pricks&quot; herself and hands you a towel to hold that had her blood on it.  You give 1000 pp to the gnome guy and you get an uncut Hyacinth.  You take this to some gemcutter in the Rathe Mnts pay him 2000 pp to get it cut.  Take all 4 items back to the gnome.  He gives you a hyacinth talism.  It's -7 str agi int and some other minus.  Take this back to the prickly pear chick.  She is so happy that you gave her this &quot;gift&quot;  She puts it on and it kills her.  You get the talism back as a Pulsating Hyacinth Talism.  Stats already said above.  HOWEVER if your a shadowknihgt you give the talism back the necro and he then summons a lvl 53 zombie =)  Supposedly a full group of 50's can easily take him out with fear/kite method.  You get the heart of this zombie take it back to the necro guy and he gives you your SK only 49 drain spell.  Drains 280 hp for 300 mana and recast time is 2-3 mins.  I have gotten all quest items exept the hyacinth and had it cut.  I'm still waiting on me being able to get a group of people big enough to take out the 53 guy.  <BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Arwenrose Soulstealer <BR>
44 Shadowknight Bertox<BR>
Shadowdark Assembly
