				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				okay im a necro thats looking to up his agi as well as keep his int at or near the 200 int range, and I did this quest. yes it actually is for the SK life leechscroll but if you're like me and want the agi this is a great item considering the difficulty of the quest. there are actually a lot of differences I noted when doing the quest than the previously mentioedn one, but then again I noticed the date is about a year ago and hell things change without verant telling us =P. anyway, first off, the guy is kazzsomething another and hes a DE necro. secondly, you have to be 50 or above or he wont talk to you (give you the quest). now, for me, the amount of plat seemed to be switched around. you give 2k (instead of 1k as mentioned in the previous post) to the DE necro questgiver guy, and he does give you an uncut hyacinth thingy. then, you take it to a gemcutter (ironically enough a gnome), and give him the stone and 1k, and he'll give you back the cut hyacinth (or something like that, exact name escapes me at the moment, but he gives the gem back slightly altered basically). give the three items (orb necklace, cut hyacinth, and blood parchment) to the quest giver and he gives you a necklace that has some crazy negative stats (something like minus 24 from wis str and another stat like stam). other than those differences I've outlined, all the details on the quest are accurate. again from the sounds of it this quest has been changed around some, which seems kinda odd that they'd change things around like that for no apparent reason. then again, this is verant we're talking about. ;)
